I'm thrilled with my purchase. I had bought a 16" laptop to replace my old, outdated iMac desktop and found myself missing the desktop terribly. I missed using a conventional wireless keyboard and mouse, and didn't feel comfortable with the laptop touchpad. I knew the solution was to raise the height of the laptop and pair my former keyboard and mouse via bluetooth. Thanks to the stand, it worked so well that I've decided to take the stand with me when I visit my home on Aruba this winter.
